# =========================
# Tooltips (Hover Text)
# =========================
option.qualityLevel.comment=Changes the overall rendering quality and sample counts.
option.HALF_RES_SSAO.comment=Runs SSAO at half resolution for better performance.
option.HALF_RES_BLOOM.comment=Runs Bloom at half resolution for better performance.
option.HALF_RES_GODRAYS.comment=Runs God Rays at half resolution for better performance.

option.shadowMapResolution.comment=Higher values mean sharper shadows, but lower FPS.
option.SHADOW_PCF_SIZE.comment=Controls how soft or blurry the shadow edges are.

option.sunIntensity.comment=Scales sunlight, sky color, and the visible sun disc.
option.SATURATION.comment=Adjusts the intensity of colors in the game.
option.CONTRAST.comment=Adjusts the difference between light and dark areas.
option.EXPOSURE_ADAPT_SPEED.comment=How fast the camera adjusts to bright or dark areas.

option.fogDensity.comment=Controls atmospheric distance fog strength.
option.SSAO_RADIUS.comment=How far the ambient occlusion spreads into corners and crevices.
option.SSAO_BIAS.comment=Prevents self-shadowing artifacts. Increase if you see weird dots.
option.AO_STRENGTH.comment=How dark the ambient occlusion shadows are.
option.bloomThreshold.comment=How bright a light source must be to start glowing.
option.BLOOM_STRENGTH.comment=How intense the glow effect is.

option.WAVING_FOLIAGE.comment=Enables or disables the waving animation for plants and leaves.
option.WATER_REFLECT.comment=Enables or disables reflections on the water surface.

